Your first lead makes your partner understand What is the chief component of your hand, And hence there is necessity the strongest That your first lead be from your suit that's longest. In this with ace and king, lead king then ace; With king and queen, king also has first place; With ace, queen, knave, lead ace, and then the queen, With ace, four small ones, ace should first be seen.
